Package org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.staging

Interface ExecutionMonitor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CoarseBoundedProgressExecutionMonitor, DynamicProcessorAssigner, ExecutionMonitor.Adapter, HumanUnderstandableExecutionMonitor, MultiExecutionMonitor, RecordStorageMigrator.BatchImporterProgressMonitor, SpectrumExecutionMonitor
    public interface ExecutionMonitor
    Gets notified now and then about StageExecution, where statistics can be read and displayed, aggregated or in other ways make sense of the data of StageExecution.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      static class  ExecutionMonitor.Adapter
      Base implementation with most methods defaulting to not doing anything.
